## Performance

### Objetivos Lighthouse
- **Performance**: >90
- **Accessibility**: >90
- **Best Practices**: >90
- **SEO**: >90

### Métricas Core Web Vitals
- **LCP** (Largest Contentful Paint): <2.5s
- **FID** (First Input Delay): <100ms
- **CLS** (Cumulative Layout Shift): <0.1

### Optimizaciones

#### Frontend
- **Code Splitting**: Lazy loading de rutas
- **Image Optimization**: WebP, lazy loading, sizes
- **Font Optimization**: Preload críticas, subset
- **CSS**: Critical CSS inline, resto lazy
- **JavaScript**: Minificación, tree shaking

#### Backend
- **Caching**: Redis para queries frecuentes
- **Database**: Índices optimizados, queries eficientes
- **API**: Response compression (gzip)
- **CDN**: Assets estáticos (Vercel/Cloudflare)

#### Monitoring
- **Real User Monitoring**: Vercel Analytics
- **Synthetic Monitoring**: Lighthouse CI
- **Alerts**: Si métricas degradan

